Lightwave MicroPython

The brand new iteration of LW.

(More info will go here at some point as well as fixing various jank)

Docker:
  Install:
    mkdir -p /tmp/lwmp ; cd /tmp/lwmp
    curl "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/GanerCodes/LWMP/refs/heads/main/Dockerfile" > ./Dockerfile
    docker build -t lwmp .

  Flash:
    docker run -it --privileged --device=/dev/bus/usb \
               --group-add dialout -v /dev:/dev \
               lwmp /bin/bash -c './flash.sh y y'

  Server:
    mkdir -p /root/LWMP/Data ; cd /root/LWMP
    docker run --net=host -v "$PWD/Data:/opt/LWMP/Server/Data" \
           lwmp /bin/bash -c "cd Server && ☾ server.☾"